@id = 1

### ─── ROLES ───────────────────────────────────────────────

### Obtener todos los roles
GET {{baseUrl}}/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Crear rol
POST {{baseUrl}}/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "role": "Administrator",
    "description": "Acceso total al sistema",
    "active": true
}

### Actualizar rol
PUT {{baseUrl}}/roles/{{id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "role": "Administrator",
    "description": "Acceso total al sistema",
    "active": true
}

### Toggle activo/inactivo
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/roles/rolToggle/{{id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "active": false
}

### Eliminar rol
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/roles/{{id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}